776
01:31:26,247 --> 01:31:29,512
<i>three blocks from our apartment.</i>

777
01:31:29,584 --> 01:31:33,520
<i>(August) My brother worked</i>
<i>in an emergency room downtown.</i>

778
01:31:33,588 --> 01:31:37,922
<i>A drug addict came in</i>
<i>with a wound to his ribs.</i>

779
01:31:37,992 --> 01:31:40,688
<i>My brother tried to dress the wound.</i>

780
01:31:41,696 --> 01:31:44,563
<i>He pulled a gun from his jacket...</i>

781
01:31:44,632 --> 01:31:48,591
<i>...then he shot my brother</i>
<i>through his left eye.</i>

782
01:31:48,670 --> 01:31:50,865
<i>(Alice) My husband, Michael,</i>

783
01:31:50,939 --> 01:31:55,308
