790
01:32:16,998 --> 01:32:22,561
<i>I teach American History</i>
<i>at the University of Pennsylvania.</i>

791
01:32:22,637 --> 01:32:25,003
<i>I have an idea...</i>

792
01:32:25,974 --> 01:32:28,807
