798
01:33:01,009 --> 01:33:03,204
Please return to your vehicle.

799
01:33:03,278 --> 01:33:05,769
<i>(Ivy)</i> What was that noise?

800
01:33:08,716 --> 01:33:12,652
What are you doing out here?
How... how'd you get here?

801
01:33:12,720 --> 01:33:15,052
Are you from the towns?

802
01:33:16,591 --> 01:33:18,115
Uh...

803
01:33:18,193 --> 01:33:20,525
Where are you from?

804
01:33:23,498 --> 01:33:26,160
The woods.

805
01:33:29,204 --> 01:33:31,968
You came from the woods?

806
01:33:34,075 --> 01:33:36,441
ln there?

807
01:33:37,545 --> 01:33:40,105
Will you help me?

808
01:33:40,748 --> 01:33:44,548
l need to find a doctor of medicine.

809
01:33:44,619 --> 01:33:46,883
l must find these things.
We must make haste.

810
01:33:46,955 --> 01:33:49,321
Listen, ma'am.

811
01:33:50,458 --> 01:33:52,790
l'm just supposed to...

812
01:34:11,212 --> 01:34:13,737
ls someone hurt?

813
01:34:15,483 --> 01:34:17,815
Please, sir. We must make haste.

814
01:34:23,258 --> 01:34:26,523
- Well, you... you live in there?
- l do, sir.

815
01:34:35,637 --> 01:34:37,867
<i>(man on radio) Breaker.</i>

816
01:34:40,041 --> 01:34:42,635
- What is your name?
- Kevin.

817
01:34:43,244 --> 01:34:45,235
Kevin.

818
01:34:46,347 --> 01:34:48,679
You have kindness in your voice.

819
01:34:50,418 --> 01:34:52,978
l did not expect that.

820
01:34:58,826 --> 01:35:02,262
We have guard shacks every ten miles
around the perimeter of the preserve.

821
01:35:02,330 --> 01:35:07,859
We keep medical supplies in there
in case of animal bites or related injuries.

822
01:35:07,935 --> 01:35:11,200
You can find the things
written on the paper?

823
01:35:12,573 --> 01:35:14,734
Uh...

824
01:35:14,809 --> 01:35:17,801
- You have to wait here.
- Please, sir.

825
01:35:17,879 --> 01:35:20,245
Please... take this as payment.

826
01:35:27,288 --> 01:35:29,756
Wait, y-you're not...

827
01:35:29,824 --> 01:35:32,588
You're not tricking me, are you?

828
01:35:32,660 --> 01:35:35,652
l do not understand.

829
01:35:37,832 --> 01:35:40,460
What's your name?

830
01:35:40,535 --> 01:35:42,526
lvy.

831
01:35:44,439 --> 01:35:47,203
