834
01:35:53,981 --> 01:35:56,176
<i>The body of seven-year-old</i>
<i>Katrina Nelson was found today.</i>

835
01:35:56,250 --> 01:35:58,309
<i>She</i>'<i>d been missing for three days.</i>

836
